'''Peter Geddis''' is an [[Wikipedia:English people|English]] stage and screen actor. In the [[1977]] [[original trilogy]] film, [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']], Geddis portrayed the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic|rebel]] officer whose neck was broken by [[Anakin Skywalker|Darth Vader]];<ref name="Making of" /> the character was later named [[Captain]] [[Raymus Antilles]].<ref name="USW">''[[Ultimate Star Wars]]''</ref>

